OL,7,FThe mother of a fisherman, who died
OL,8,Falongside his crewmate, says she still
OL,9,Fhas unanswered questions, four years
OL,10,Fafter his death.
OL,12,FRobert Morley and Adam Harper were
OL,13,Fworking on the fishing boat the Joanna
OL,14,FC when it sank five miles off the
OL,15,FSussex coast.
OL,17,FRobert who was ship's mate and Adam
OL,18,Fwho was the deckhand drowned when
OL,19,Ftheir boat capsized in Newhaven in
OL,20,FNovember 2020 - the captain survived.
