OL,7,FThe company that owns the boat, Laura
OL,8,FD Fishing, has been ordered to pay
OL,9,Fmore than #100,000 in fines and costs
OL,10,Ffollowing an investigation into the
OL,11,Fincident.
OL,13,FHowever, Jackie Woodford, Robert's
OL,14,Fmother, says she does not believe the
OL,15,Fboat's owner is solely accountable and
OL,16,Fstill feels many questions remain
OL,17,Fabout the sinking.
