OL,7,FMs Woodford said: "Robert was happy-go-
OL,8,Flucky, not a care in the world. I
OL,9,Falways called him my Peter Pan, the
OL,10,Fboy who wouldn't grow up, and he won't
OL,11,Fnow.
OL,13,F"We haven't had answers, not the
OL,14,Fanswers that we wanted - the 'how?',
OL,15,Fthe 'why?' and the 'what?'
OL,17,F"As far as (the investigation) was
OL,18,Fconcerned, the 'how?' was and the
OL,19,F'why?' was because of the stability of
OL,20,Fthe boat.
