OL,7,F"But we have no answers as to how that
OL,8,Fboat got into that position."
OL,10,FKatie Barrett, Robert's sister said:
OL,11,F"We've had to kind of create our own
OL,12,Fclosure because the closure we were
OL,13,Fhoping for we're never going to get.
OL,15,F"So what we have to do at this stage
OL,16,Fis find a way to deal with that within
OL,17,Four family and then move forward,
OL,18,Fbecause also Robert wouldn't want us
OL,19,Fstuck in the past."
