OL,7,FAdam Harper was trapped inside the
OL,8,Fboat as it sank. The body of Robert
OL,9,FMorley was found washed up near
OL,10,FBexhill three weeks later.
OL,12,FAn investigation into the tragedy
OL,13,Ffound that the scallop dredger
OL,14,Fcapsized after its gear became snagged
OL,15,Fon the seabed.
OL,17,FThe Maritime and Coastguard Agency
OL,18,F(MCA) said: "Joanna C, owned by Laura
OL,19,FD Fishing, had undergone a major refit
OL,20,Fin 2019. These modifications, affected
OL,21,Fthe stability of the vessel.
