OL,7,F"Extensive changes made to Joanna C,
OL,8,Fwere not approved by the MCA, and made
OL,9,Fit significantly non-compliant with
OL,10,Fthe minimum standards of stability."
OL,12,FThe company, Laura D Fishing, pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to failing to take all
OL,14,Freasonable steps to ensure that the
OL,15,Fvessel was operated in a safe manner.
